_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59093</s:story_id></item><item><title>Gold &amp; Blue Enterprises Launches GBE Partner Network</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/11/general-gold-blue-enterprises-launches-gbe-partner-network</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/11/general-gold-blue-enterprises-launches-gbe-partner-network</guid><category>General</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Gold and Blue Enterprises Launches GBE Partner Network" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/11/GBE26_PartnerNetwork_1920x1080.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – Gold & Blue Enterprises has announced the launch of the GBE Partner Network, an alliance designed to connect businesses with growth, while providing opportunities to strengthen West Virginia University Athletics.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/11/GBE26_PartnerNetwork_1920x1080.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/11/GBE26_PartnerNetwork_1920x1080.jpg"><media:title>Gold and Blue Enterprises Launches GBE Partner Network</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/11/GBE26_PartnerNetwork_1920x1080.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 10:00:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>3</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59092</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Complete Sweep of No. 7 Kansas</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/10/baseball-mountaineers-complete-sweep-of-no-7-kansas</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/10/baseball-mountaineers-complete-sweep-of-no-7-kansas</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Reese Bassinger celebrates after getting the final out against No. 7 Kansas" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/10/05102026_WVBB_JCG_45.jpg" /><br /><br />LAWRENCE, Kan. – The No. 15 West Virginia University baseball team finished off the sweep over No. 7 Kansas on Sunday at Hoglund Ballpark with a 13-2, eight-inning victory. The Mountaineers improve to 35-12 and 19-8 in the Big 12 while the Jayhawks fall to 37-15 and 20-7 in league play.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/10/05102026_WVBB_JCG_45.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/10/05102026_WVBB_JCG_45.jpg"><media:title>Reese Bassinger celebrates after getting the final out against No. 7 Kansas</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/10/05102026_WVBB_JCG_45.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 17:05:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59091</s:story_id></item><item><title>Final Home Meet Brings Multiple Wins for WVU</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/9/track-field-final-home-meet-brings-multiple-wins-for-wvu</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/9/track-field-final-home-meet-brings-multiple-wins-for-wvu</guid><category>Track &amp; Field</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="The Track & Field seniors honored during the WVU Last Chance Meet" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/9/20260503_BASE_WVUvsKansasState_TT-4126.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University track and field team hosted the WVU Last Chance Meet on Saturday in Morgantown, earning